The changes which are reverasble are called physical change and the changes which which cannot be reversed are called 
chemical change.

A chemical change is also called chemical reaction. 

Metals are substance which donate a electron.

The substance which accept electrons are called non-metals.

If the atom of the substamnce has electron value of 1, 2 or 3 in the last cell, it donates electricity and is a metal

